<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="es">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <title>BookHive - Menú de Autores</title>
    <style>
        body {
            margin: 0;
            font-family: 'Segoe UI', Tahoma, Geneva, Verdana, sans-serif;
            background: linear-gradient(145deg, #e8f5e9, #f1f8f4);
        }

        header {
            display: flex;
            justify-content: space-between;
            align-items: center;
            padding: 8px 15px;
            background: #3F7D58;
            box-shadow: 0 2px 5px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.05);
        }

        .logo img {
            height: 35px;
        }

        .nav-links a {
            margin: 0 15px;
            text-decoration: none;
            color: white;
            font-weight: 500;
        }

        .main {
            text-align: center;
            padding: 70px 20px 40px;
            min-height: 100vh;
        }

            .main h1 {
                font-size: 2.8em;
                color: #1b5e20;
                margin-bottom: 10px;
            }

            .main p {
                font-size: 1.2em;
                color: #4a4a4a;
                margin-bottom: 40px;
            }

        .cards {
            display: flex;
            justify-content: center;
            gap: 40px;
            flex-wrap: wrap;
        }

        .card {
            background: white;
            width: 280px;
            padding: 30px 25px;
            border-radius: 15px;
            box-shadow: 0 4px 15px rgba(0,0,0,0.1);
            transition: transform 0.2s;
            display: flex;
            flex-direction: column;
            align-items: center;
        }

            .card:hover {
                transform: scale(1.05);
            }

        .card-icon {
            font-size: 60px;
            color: #43a047;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
        }

        .card h3 {
            margin: 0;
            color: #2e7d32;
            font-size: 1.6em;
            margin-bottom: 15px;
        }

        .card p {
            color: #555;
            font-size: 1em;
            margin-bottom: 25px;
            text-align: center;
        }

        .card a.button {
            background-color: #43a047;
            color: white;
            padding: 12px 25px;
            border-radius: 25px;
            text-decoration: none;
            font-weight: bold;
            font-size: 1em;
            transition: background-color 0.3s;
        }

            .card a.button:hover {
                background-color: #388e3c;
            }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="main">
        <h1>Menú de Autores</h1>
        <p>Gestiona los autores registrados en BookHive</p>
        <div class="cards">
            <div class="card">
                <div class="card-icon">🧑‍🎓</div>
                <h3>Crear Autor</h3>
                <p>Registra un nuevo autor en el sistema.</p>
                <a href="/Authors/Create" class="button" aria-label="Crear Autor">Crear</a>
            </div>
            <div class="card">
                <div class="card-icon">📋</div>
                <h3>Listar Autores</h3>
                <p>Consulta la lista completa de autores.</p>
                <a href="/Authors/Index" class="button" aria-label="Listar Autores">Listar</a>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</body>
</html>